  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="545432535">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-545432535" class="vote-count">1</span>
              <a id="btn-545432535" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="545432535">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/namik_ercan/">namik_ercan</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/545432535">2012-08-13 01:19:53</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">村上春樹的《旋轉木馬鏖戰記》不在其最有名的代表作之列，倒因阿爾沙文在歐洲杯上讀這書而引起我閱讀興趣。譯者林少華說這是作者寫《挪威的森林》的準備之作，收錄8個短篇，一如書名，這些故事說的是人生如何在反覆出現的情景里掙扎，猶如乘著不停轉的旋轉木馬打仗，只是限於篇幅行文顯得拘束，4顆星</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1000594/?comment_id=545432535"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1044176459">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-1044176459" class="vote-count">1</span>
              <a id="btn-1044176459" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1044176459">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/RamblER/">正在学习</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/1044176459">2016-05-22 15:58:31</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">从「游泳池畔」找到的。村上春树应该是集合了近现代多个作家的影响，反正此书中每篇都带有一期一会寂静涅槃的味道，结局没有圆满的，用旋转木马来描述人生也不无道理。所谓鏖战，应该指的是每个人与自己内心的较量吧。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1000594/?comment_id=1044176459"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="273924005">
